{"tid":478060,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"挺起胸膛引女埋身　吳業坤惹女學生歡呼","createTime":"2017-11-23T16:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T15:37:57.000Z","uid":35964,"like":3,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"450640bfbe5ac8c2628f869cd58a26fa01d1a04a","tid":478060,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T16:11:17.000Z","msg":"藝人吳業坤在秀茂坪一間女校宣傳無綫台慶劇《誇世代》，一出場時更獲女學生歡呼吶喊，十足一個「妹妹殺手」。訪問時，他坦言之前亦去過女校：「當時係出席School Tour，入女校係每個男學生嘅夢想！」<br />\n<br />\n吳業坤又指讀書時鄰校是女校，見到一班班女學生出出入入好開心：「我每次經過佢哋面前都會挺起胸膛，但始終一個女仔都識唔到。（睇你唔上眼？）都係！（依家威番次？）佢哋鍾意我唱歌咋！（依家快啲識番個？）佢哋太細個喇！未成年唔好教壞佢哋，娛樂圈係大染缸，唔好向佢哋灌輸啲錯誤&hellip;&hellip;係未必要嘅知識先啱。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171123/photo/bkn-20171123164326725-1123_00862_001_04b.jpg?20171123181904\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171123%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171123164326725-1123_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20171123181904&h=8544a057&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"988a4d97d3e5c6d5f1d2fc1c5e8cd216e25204b7","tid":478060,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225ef288d9c136ce7c8ce9f91c88d94bfbe9ca16","tid":478060,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T23:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bbb933bf71a1a5ccd4176148692257b14b8649","tid":478060,"uid":59961,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:23:59.000Z","msg":"次次訪問都同溝女有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd66379315666fc6362d106ebc7bc166f11ba05b","tid":478060,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:25:04.000Z","msg":"養狐仙。。。"},{"pid":"fd7556b8fcbb5af3fa3e8123a6b82ca190429058","tid":478060,"uid":50162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"reply